                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns" data-equalizer-watch>
                <div class="panel radius callout" data-equalizer-watch>
                    <h5><strong>Why ARiiP?</strong></h5>
                    <p>
                       ARiiP provides an efficient and fast mechanism to extract, combine and filter from the input files and can provide a simple HTML report as output, with the detected transactions.
                    </p>
